introduction: Britain and Ireland's Next Top Model, Cycle 9 is the ninth and final cycle of Britain & Ireland's Next Top Model. It began to air on 20 June 2013. This cycle once again features fashion model Elle Macpherson as executive producer and host of the show alongside a judging panel consisting of Tyson Beckford and Dannii Minogue.Former judges Whitney Port and Julien Macdonald did not come back for the new series.
